name: MoonMix
description:
This is a model that incorporates Anything4.5, AbyssOrangeMix2, Counterfeit-V2.5, and a few others.
It doesn't need a long negative prompt, it generates relatively good hands, it performs better at higher resolutions, and of course it works at lower resolutions.It is also capable of generating nsfw images.
All the previews you see do not use Controlnet, LoRA, Hires fix.
(Of course, I would Recommend that you use EasyNegative, badhandv4, or similar Negative Embedding, and the Hires fix can be adjusted to suit your needs.)
I integrated this VAE: kl-f8-anime2, which makes the generated images more vibrant than using animevae.
I only tested this sampler with Euler a. If you find it works better with other samplers please let me know.
If you like this model, please give me a like, thanks!
